snippet.textDisplay:
Best cricket song so far.
Way better than waahy waahy and current ICC World Cup anthem.
It has emotions, style, rythem, faaris shafi and the legend Atif Aslam.
Then that last line..
Mitti da maan tu rakh lay gives goosebumps to every Pakistani fan who has seen all the sufferings we've had for so many years.
❣️❣️❣️
